data.description: Solid as a rock 3/2/2 brick home with an extra lot in a beautiful established neighborhood Morgan's Point. Uniquely beautiful curb appeal with lots of room to roam. Walk into a massive living/dining area with lots of natural light and a large brick fireplace. Pretty kitchen with granite countertops, lots of cabinets and a lovely breakfast bar. Large master suite with access to an adjoining sunroom. Master suite also boasts a large walk-in closet and a master bathroom. All bedrooms are flooded with natural light with well thought out raised windows sills. Large sunroom with lots of windows that would make a great office or playroom. Massive, connected carport with a large storeroom and raised ceilings. The great outdoors is a treat with a large extra lot suitable for building. 2 storage sheds, live oak trees and no neighbors behind you. Nice rock patio and walkways. This home is ready to be fixed up just the way you want it. Roof replaced May 2023. Belton ISD. Close to local restaurants and Belton Lake.
